    <problem id="fs-id2856011">
      <para id="fs-id2856013">The lengths and diameters of four wires are given as shown.</para><figure id="fs-id2856016"><label/><media id="fs-id3189530" alt="The figure shows four cylinders representing sections of wire. The length and diameter of the wires are indicated graphically and with labels below. The wires labeled 2L are the same length and twice as long as the wires labeled L. The wires labeled 2D are twice as thick as the wires labeled D. Wire 1: 2L, D (long, thin). Wire 2: L, D (short, thin). Wire 3: 2L, 2D (long, thick). Wire 4: L, 2D (short, thick).">
